How should I put it?

00:17:12.060 --> 00:17:13.060
When I was nine,

00:17:15.500 --> 00:17:16.740
my mother left me.

00:17:17.980 --> 00:17:19.340
On the day she left,

00:17:20.260 --> 00:17:21.700
