00:17:23.620 --> 00:17:24.740
begging her not to go.

00:17:24.740 --> 00:17:26.940
But in the end, she walked away.

00:17:33.380 --> 00:17:34.580
And after that?

00:17:36.380 --> 00:17:38.380
My dad and I relied on each other.

00:17:40.100 --> 00:17:41.860
Even though I didn't have a mother,

00:17:42.940 --> 00:17:44.860
I got all of my father's love.

00:17:48.340 --> 00:17:49.340
I know my dad would give

00:17:49.340 --> 00:17:50.780
absolutely everything for me,

00:17:51.700 --> 00:17:53.700
so even without my mother,

00:17:53.700 --> 00:17:54.340
my dad

00:17:54.940 --> 00:17:56.100
made sure I felt like

00:17:56.100 --> 00:17:58.140
growing up in a complete

00:17:58.500 --> 00:17:59.140
and warm home.

00:18:00.580 --> 00:18:02.140
Back then, I always believed

00:18:02.820 --> 00:18:03.380
that in this lifetime,

00:18:04.100 --> 00:18:05.300
I'd never be separated from my dad.

00:18:17.860 --> 00:18:18.940
Want to hear more?

00:18:24.100 --> 00:18:24.620
Alright.

00:18:25.380 --> 00:18:26.140
I'll tell you everything.

00:18:30.660 --> 00:18:31.900
Twelve years ago,

00:18:34.140 --> 00:18:35.700
something terrible happened.

00:18:37.340 --> 00:18:38.860
My dad suddenly

00:18:39.860 --> 00:18:40.780
left me.

00:18:42.540 --> 00:18:43.660
And not long after that,

00:18:45.340 --> 00:18:46.660
the person I loved most in my life

00:18:46.660 --> 00:18:47.780
left me too.

00:18:49.660 --> 00:18:51.060
Suddenly, I had nothing.

00:18:52.740 --> 00:18:54.100
My whole world collapsed.

00:18:55.100 --> 00:18:56.100
Living was hard,

00:18:57.940 --> 00:18:59.300
and I was lost.

00:19:00.700 --> 00:19:01.900
When I wanted to give up,

00:19:01.900 --> 00:19:03.140
Ms. Zhuang told me...

00:19:04.340 --> 00:19:05.340
Right now, you feel like

00:19:05.980 --> 00:19:07.660
the whole world has abandoned you,

00:19:08.100 --> 00:19:09.580
but that's just how you feel.

00:19:10.860 --> 00:19:12.340
Besides, don't forget,

00:19:12.860 --> 00:19:13.860
no matter what,

00:19:14.340 --> 00:19:15.780
you at least still have ballet.

00:19:16.500 --> 00:19:17.780
You're

00:19:18.060 --> 00:19:19.100
an excellent ballerina.

00:19:20.020 --> 00:19:21.860
You're still that girl
who can't be crushed.

00:19:21.900 --> 00:19:22.340
Right?

00:19:23.060 --> 00:19:25.300
So I put on my ballet shoes
without hesitation.

00:19:26.420 --> 00:19:27.340
No music,

00:19:27.780 --> 00:19:28.780
no choreography,

00:19:30.100 --> 00:19:32.100
only the pain and cries from within.

00:19:36.100 --> 00:19:37.180
After that period of time,

00:19:37.180 --> 00:19:38.340
I felt

00:19:38.860 --> 00:19:39.820
life was kind to me.

00:19:39.820 --> 00:19:40.700
I was fortunate.

00:19:41.580 --> 00:19:42.660
We'll encounter

00:19:42.660 --> 00:19:43.900
various problems and difficulties.

00:19:44.380 --> 00:19:45.860
Many times, there are no solutions.

00:19:46.660 --> 00:19:48.700
But as long as I can dance,

00:19:49.100 --> 00:19:50.660
I feel like I'm truly alive.

00:19:51.700 --> 00:19:52.660
Ballet

00:19:54.100 --> 00:19:55.340
gave me a way to live.

00:19:59.180 --> 00:20:01.580
During the darkest days of my life,

00:20:02.900 --> 00:20:04.860
ballet was like a brilliant beam

00:20:05.780 --> 00:20:06.900
of light,

00:20:07.260 --> 00:20:08.420
shining into my world.

00:20:08.900 --> 00:20:10.860
It turned my black-and-white life

00:20:11.860 --> 00:20:12.780
into a colorful one.

00:20:16.660 --> 00:20:18.260
So dance requires experience.

00:20:20.140 --> 00:20:21.380
If not for that experience,

00:20:22.860 --> 00:20:24.780
I wouldn't have been here

00:20:25.580 --> 00:20:26.940
and talked to you today.

00:20:36.660 --> 00:20:37.780
The atmosphere here is quite nice.

00:20:40.140 --> 00:20:40.860
I'm happy.

00:20:43.140 --> 00:20:43.900
Me too.

