That such a serious disaster has drawn

00:37:43.660 --> 00:37:45.100
so many friends willing to help.

00:37:45.100 --> 00:37:46.700
I'm truly touched.

00:37:47.420 --> 00:37:48.540
We're all friends.

00:37:48.740 --> 00:37:49.420
No need for formalities.

00:37:50.100 --> 00:37:52.020
You're being too modest.

00:37:52.580 --> 00:37:53.020
Mr. Feng,

00:37:53.260 --> 00:37:54.220
we did that

00:37:54.220 --> 00:37:55.580
because of your personal charisma.

00:37:56.100 --> 00:37:57.020
That's absolutely true.

00:37:57.420 --> 00:37:58.980
When we faced difficulties,

00:37:59.100 --> 00:38:00.500
you didn't hesitate for a second

00:38:00.740 --> 00:38:03.020
and helped us find outlets
for our grapes.

00:38:03.100 --> 00:38:04.540
Now that you're in trouble,

00:38:04.580 --> 00:38:06.540
we have to help you
even if we're not selling anything.

00:38:07.420 --> 00:38:08.140
Well said.

00:38:08.460 --> 00:38:09.020
Mr. Feng,

00:38:09.260 --> 00:38:11.900
as the most authoritative
wine publication

00:38:12.060 --> 00:38:13.620
in the country,

00:38:13.940 --> 00:38:16.100
we set high standards

