like yours.

00:42:20.940 --> 00:42:22.620
Your raw material cultivation technology

00:42:22.620 --> 00:42:23.900
is more mature than ours.

00:42:24.300 --> 00:42:25.660
Let's collaborate on a new wine,

00:42:26.060 --> 00:42:27.900
and we'll call it Huacan Cygne.

00:42:28.620 --> 00:42:29.300
That's a great idea!

00:42:29.940 --> 00:42:30.660
This will work!

00:42:31.140 --> 00:42:32.020
The wine will be a great success.

00:42:32.420 --> 00:42:33.300
Come on. I'd like to make a toast.

00:42:33.980 --> 00:42:36.460
This is a powerhouse partnership.

00:42:36.580 --> 00:42:37.020
Deal!

00:42:37.420 --> 00:42:38.500
- A powerhouse partnership.
- Indeed!

00:42:39.420 --> 00:42:40.020
Sir,

00:42:40.060 --> 00:42:42.100
the documentary just aired,

